3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses deep learning techniques to perform semantic segmentation and object recognition, which are tasks related to artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics): The paper deals with 3D data such as reconstructed point clouds and CAD models, which are commonly used in computer graphics.
